Antoine Chappey https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Antoine_Chappey 0 Antoine Chappey (born 1960) is a French actor. He has appeared in over 80 films and television shows since 1989. He starred in the film Nelly, which was screened in the Un Certain Regard section at the 2004 Cannes Film Festival. Antoine_Chappey ( born 1960 ) is a_French_actor .
